As a student:
    I want a clear, branded homepage that serves as the entry point to event discovery, making it easy to start searching and browsing.
    I want to easily browse all published events and use search and filter tools so I can quickly find activities that interest me.
    I want a clear button to claim my ticket, and if the event is paid, I need to be directed to a payment method placeholder.
    after claiming a ticket, I want to immediately see a digital ticket with a unique QR code so I can use it for check-in at the even
    I want a clear button on the event details page to easily add the event to my preferred digital calendar
As a user:
    I want the student-facing website to look and function perfectly so I can use it easily while on the go.
